OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be cloudy with occasional rain or
OL,7,Fdrizzle. Then becoming clearer in the
OL,8,Fearly hours with a few light passing
OL,9,Fshowers. Fresh southwesterly winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CFriday:FMostly cloudy throughout the
OL,12,Fday with the chance of a few light
OL,13,Fshowers. Rain will spread eastwards
OL,14,Fduring the evening. Fresh west to
OL,15,Fsouthwesterly winds.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FEarly
OL,18,Frain on Saturday clearing to sunny
OL,19,Fspells and a few showers. Breezy on
OL,20,FSunday and Monday with a chance of
OL,21,Fshowers, these mainly across Shetland.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
